{title: Blossoms In The Springtime}
{artist: Hank Snow}
{composer: Written by Vaughn Horton}

[G]When I see blossoms in the [D7]springtime
I know that sweetheart time is [G]here
My love that blossoms in the [D7]springtime
Blooms in my heart through all the [G]year
[C]I love the blossoms in the [G]springtime
[D7]Kissed by the sunshine and the [G]rain
[C]I love to hold you oh my [G]darling
[D7]When kisses bloom in sweetheart's [G]lane
Sometimes a spark of love may [D7]smolder
